title.en: Members of Merched y Wawr Rhumney Valley Branch 2010
title.cy: Aelodau Merched y Wawr Cangen Cwm Rhymni 2010

description.en:
Aelodau Cangen Cwm Rhymni a fu’n gwrando ar Elin Jones yn siarad ar bwysigrwydd y ferch yng Nghapel Siloh, Ystrad Mynach, Mai 19, 2010
O’r chwith i’r dde – Mari Mills, Eirlys Thomas, Gaynor Williams, Janet Cumpstone, Mair Roberts, Marian Fairclough, Sian John, Jenni Jones Annett, Elin Jones, Wilma Davies, Maureen Potter, Evelyn Williams, Eleri Betts, Lena Morgan
